rtal or mobile app. At the scheduled time they log in and join securely. Providers see the appointment in their calendar, access the patient's health record during the call, take notes, and create consultation documents, prescriptions, or lab orders afterward.\"},{\"question\":\"Do patients and providers receive reminders about video consultations?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Automated reminders are sent for scheduled telemedicine appointments, payments, and follow-ups. Notifications can be delivered by email, SMS, or push to reduce no-shows and keep everyone prepared.\"},{\"question\":\"Do patients need special apps for telemedicine visits?\",\"answer\":\"No. Patients simply log in through your branded patient portal or mobile app. Telehealth video consultations run directly inside the Virtual Practice—no third-party downloads required.\"},{\"question\":\"Can I bill for telehealth visits the same way as in-person consultations?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Telemedicine appointments are defined like in-person services. You can set duration, service charges, and taxes; patients pay online; and billing records are generated automatically.\"},{\"question\":\"What happens to notes from a video consultation?\",\"answer\":\"Notes taken during the video consultation are stored in the encounter log. Providers can use them to generate consultation documents, prescriptions, or lab orders. If AI Scribe is used, these notes are included as context for creating clinical documentation.\"},{\"question\":\"Can more than one person join a telemedicine call?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Providers can invite caregivers, translators, or additional participants for instant video calls. An assisted video mode also lets nurses or staff help patients in remote areas connect to their provider.\"},{\"question\":\"Are telehealth video consultations secure and compliant?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. All telemedicine visits are encrypted and compliant with HIPAA, GDPR, and other healthcare regulations. White-labelling is optional—you may keep the standard look or customize the portal and apps to reflect your brand.\"},{\"question\":\"What equipment do patients need for telehealth visits?\",\"answer\":\"A smartphone, tablet, or computer with a camera and a reliable internet connection is sufficient. No extra hardware is required for most video consultations.\"}],\"product\":{\"name\":\"Virtual Practice Video Consultations\",\"alternateName\":\"Telehealth \u0026 Telemedicine Platform\",\"brand\":\"ContinuousCare\",\"description\":\"ContinuousCare Virtual Practice enables secure telehealth and telemedicine video consultations for clinics, small practices, and digital health startups. Patients can book, pay, and join online visits through web or mobile apps, while providers manage scheduling, billing, and health records in one integrated system.\",\"category\":\"Telehealth Software\",\"audience\":\"Healthcare providers, Clinics, Digital Health Startups\",\"keywords\":\"telehealth, telemedicine, video consultations, virtual care platform, healthcare SaaS, remote patient care\"}},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"Telehealth Video Consultation Software: \",\"title_highlight\":\"Professional Care\",\"title_suffix\":\" Anywhere\",\"subtitle\":\"Deliver care through secure telemedicine visits, fully integrated with appointments, billing, and health records in your Virtual Practice.\",\"cta_text\":\"Start Free Trial\",\"image_alt\":\"Healthcare provider conducting AI Scribe video consultation\"},\"problem_section\":{\"title\":\"Why Video Consultations Matter\",\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Accessible Telehealth Anywhere\",\"description\":\"Patients don't have to delay care or rely only on digital tools — secure telemedicine visits make it easy to connect from anywhere.\"},{\"title\":\"Stronger Patient Relationships\",\"description\":\"Stay connected between visits with trusted telehealth guidance and ongoing communication.\"},{\"title\":\"Future-Ready Practice\",\"description\":\"Offer flexible telemedicine services alongside in-person care, keeping your practice modern in the age of AI.\"}]},\"seamless_access\":{\"badge\":\"Seamless Patient Access\",\"title\":\"Seamless Patient Access\",\"subtitle\":\"Patients book and pay for video visits through the portal or app, then simply log in and join the call at appointment time.\",\"features\":[\"Patients book and pay for video visits through the portal or app.\",\"At the appointment time, they simply log in and join the call.\",\"Providers see video consultations on their schedule like any other service.\"],\"image_alt\":\"Patient booking and accessing video consultation through portal\"},\"clinical_workflow\":{\"badge\":\"Integrated Clinical Workflow\",\"title\":\"Integrated Clinical Workflow\",\"subtitle\":\"Complete clinical documentation with notes, prescriptions, and billing seamlessly integrated into your existing workflow.\",\"features\":[\"Providers can view the patient's health record during the call.\",\"Take notes in real-time, which flow into the encounter log.\",\"After the call, create consultation documents, prescriptions, or lab orders.\",\"Notes are available to AI Scribe if used to generate consultation documents.\"],\"image_alt\":\"Integrated clinical workflow during video consultation\"},\"consultation_options\":{\"badge\":\"Flexible Consultation Options\",\"title\":\"Flexible Consultation Options\",\"subtitle\":\"Support different types of consultations from scheduled visits to instant calls and assisted video modes for various patient needs.\",\"options\":[{\"title\":\"Scheduled Visits\",\"description\":\"Defined by service duration (e.g., 15 or 30 minutes) with the ability to extend.\"},{\"title\":\"Instant Calls\",\"description\":\"Quick, no-appointment calls with optional extra participants (caregivers, translators, etc.).\"},{\"title\":\"Assisted Video Mode\",\"description\":\"Nurses or staff can help patients in remote or low-tech locations join calls with providers.\"}],\"image_alt\":\"Flexible video c